MENU FILE HEADER (Don't delete)
MENU FILE NAME: $popcontrib/x/xved/doit_menus/replace
When prompted in the other window, type
two strings separated by the delimiter.
Global replace (nested)                     !!      ENTER 'gs/'
Global replace(unnested = whole words)      !!      ENTER 'gs"'
Replace in range                            !!      ENTER 'gsr/'
Replace in range(unnested)                  !!      ENTER 'gsr"'
Replace in line                             !!      ENTER 'gsl/'
Replace in line(unnested)                   !!      ENTER 'gsl"'
Replace in procedure                        !!      ENTER 'gsp/'
Replace in proc(unnested)                   !!      ENTER 'gsr"'
Get help                                    !!      'help vedsearch'
Search menu     ---->                       !!      'menu search'
Menu menu       ---->                       !!      'menu menu'
